SKYGBOOK (version 1.0 stable)
-----------------------------

Require:PHP (5.0 or above),apache web server.

Possibilities:
-Antispam Filter
-BB codes
-Use files for administration commands.
-Use smiles
-Use templates
-IP Ban 
-Use design in CSS

-----------------------------

Structure:
403.php 404.php - errors
captcha.php - antispan Filter
functions.php - main core
hard.php - form template
index.php - main file
template.php - if banned include this file
unlink.php - file for cron to run every 10 min
captcha/ - include antispan images
smiles/ - smiles path
text/ - for everything else
	ac.ttf - font for antispan
	banlist - ip ban
	config - main config file
	css.css - design file
	prebanlist - include ( name | ip | date ) .To ban this user 				add his ip into ban list.
	records - all records
	tmp/ - HTML template files 
	manual/ - path to manual files
	img/ - main form images

-----------------------------

Install:
1.Put files into server folder.
2.Run
	chmod -R 664 "path_to_folder"
3.Done.

